      <title>房地产公司 Adler 希望以高达 47% 的折扣出售资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/property-firm-adler-looks-to-sell-assets-at-up-to-47-discount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿德勒集团 (Adler Group SA) 请求其债券持有人允许以比不到两年前的估值低 47% 的价格出售一处未完工的公寓开发项目，因为这家陷入困境的房东竞相偿还巨额债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/property-firm-adler-looks-to-sell-assets-at-up-to-47-discount</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:29:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于电视前景恶化，派拉蒙债务被削减至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/paramount-debt-is-cut-to-junk-on-deteriorating-outlook-for-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级公司将派拉蒙全球公司的债务评级下调至垃圾级，该评级机构称，由于该公司的广播和有线电视业务持续下滑，现金流面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/paramount-debt-is-cut-to-junk-on-deteriorating-outlook-for-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:43:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
